OL,3,CHeathrow Airport fire: What went wrong?
OL,5,FITV News Science Correspondent Martin
OL,6,FStew takes a look at what went wrong
OL,7,Fat Heathrow Airport
OL,9,FThousands of flights around the world
OL,10,Fhave been disrupted after a fire at an
OL,11,Felectrical substation forced Heathrow
OL,12,FAirport to close.
OL,14,FThe fire has affected more than 1,300
OL,15,Fflights, a complete shutdown of the
OL,16,FUK's busiest airport and left
OL,17,Fthousands of homes without electricity.
