OL,3,CHeathrow Airport fire: What went wrong?
OL,5,FMore than 200,000 passengers have had
OL,6,Ftheir flights to or from the airport
OL,7,Fcancelled and more than 100 people in
OL,8,Fthe fire's immediate vicinity needed
OL,9,Fto be evacuated.
OL,11,FSpeaking to Good Morning Britain,
OL,12,Ftravel expert Simon Calder says the
OL,13,Fscale of the disruption is comparable
OL,14,Fto the volcanic ash clouds of 2010
OL,15,Fwhich shuttered UK and European
OL,16,Fairspace.
OL,18,FAnd, it is thought Heathrow will take
OL,19,Fdays to get flight services back to
OL,20,Fnormal.
