OL,3,CHeathrow Airport fire: What went wrong?
OL,5,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband told ITV
OL,6,FNews 'it's too early to say what the
OL,7,Fprecise cause of this (fire) was'
OL,9,FThe lack of resilience for Europe's
OL,10,Fbusiest airport is embarrassing and
OL,11,Fcostly.
OL,13,FAccording to Energy Secretary Ed
OL,14,FMiliband: "There are backup mechanisms
OL,15,Fin place but given the scale of this
OL,16,Ffire the backup mechanisms also seem
OL,17,Fto have been affected...
