OL,3,CHeathrow Airport fire: What went wrong?
OL,5,FThere was a backup generator but that
OL,6,Fwas also affected by the fire which
OL,7,Fgives a sense of how unusual and
OL,8,Funprecedented it was."
OL,10,FPower can be rediverted around the
OL,11,Fgrid (which explains how 62,000 homes
OL,12,Fgot their power back) but some areas
OL,13,Fincluding Heathrow rely on electricity
OL,14,Fflowing through that particular
OL,15,Fsubstation.
