OL,3,CHeathrow Airport fire: What went wrong?
OL,5,FEven once all power is restored it is
OL,6,Flikely to take days to get services
OL,7,Fback to normal.
OL,9,FThe last time we saw disruption this
OL,10,Fsevere was the result of the volcanic
OL,11,Fash cloud 15 years ago. That had an
OL,12,Fimpact across all of Europe and was
OL,13,Festimated to cost the aviation
OL,14,Findustry #130 million per day of
OL,15,Fdisruption.
